<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-deposit">How to Deposit</h3>
<h4 id="a-there-are-two-options-offered-to-make-a-deposit-">A. There are two options offered to make a deposit.</h4>
<ol>
<li><p>Pay using a Bank Card</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Step 1: Enter your ATM Card number, Expiry date, CVV (CVV is the three-digit code behind your card) and the amount you wish to deposit into your account in the given text fields. Then, click on the &quot;Deposit&quot; button.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Step 2: Enter your PIN, Bank Token or OTP which might be sent to your mobile phone (depends on the Verification method used) and complete the transaction.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Step 3: You have successfully funded your SportyBet account! Click the button or link below the page which describes the transaction as being successful and you will be redirected to another page.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>Pay using a Bank Account</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Step 1: Select your Bank Name, Account Number and the amount you wish to deposit into your account in the given text fields. Then, click on the &quot;Deposit&quot; Button.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Step 2: Enter your Birthday Date or OTP which might be sent to your mobile phone (depends on the Verification method used) and complete the transaction.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Step 3: You have successfully funded your SportyBet account! Click the button or link below the page which describes the transaction as being successful and you will be redirected to another page.</p>
<p>SportyBet pays all your fees so that all deposits are completely free!</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
