<h4 id="what-types-of-bank-cards-and-bank-accounts-are-accepted-by-our-service-">What types of Bank Cards and Bank Accounts are accepted by our service?</h4>
<p>In what relates to Bank Cards, customers can make deposits using bank cards such as Visa, Mastercard and Verve.</p>
<p>In what relates to Bank Accounts, customers can make deposits using accounts from any of the following banks: Access Bank, ALAT by WEMA, Diamond Bank, Fidelity Bank, First Bank of Nigeria, First City Monument Bank, Guaranty Trust Bank (GT Bank) and Zenith Bank.</p>
<h4 id="what-are-the-limits-for-deposits-and-how-much-does-the-charge-fee-cost-">What are the limits for Deposits and how much does the Charge Fee cost?</h4>
<ol>
<li>Minimun per transaction is NGN 100.00.</li>
<li>Maximun per transaction is NGN 9,999,999.00.</li>
<li>All Deposits are free of charges.</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="how-long-does-it-take-for-the-transaction-to-be-processed-and-for-the-deposited-sum-to-arrive-into-an-account-">How long does it take for the transaction to be processed and for the deposited sum to arrive into an account?</h4>
<p>Transactions are processed immediately. If your Balance remains unchanged, please check your transactions for more details. If you are still unable to find more information, please contact our SportyBet&#39;s Customer Service team at any time.</p>
